      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This collection contains American writer Ann Beattie's
         introduction to "Best American Short Stories, 1987," as well
         as two undated letters from Beattie to Robie Macauley
         regarding Peter Taylor; vacation plans; a new novel by Valerie
         Martin [ 
         <title render="italic">The recent martyr</title>]; Beattie's
         introduction for "Best American short stories, 1987"; and her
         request that copies of the book be sent to the people on an
         enclosed list.</p>
      </scopecontent>
